    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I have a map, an input field and the hits below the input field. After the site finishes loading, it shows me the first 10 results which is the expected behaviour. Those infos are coming from one index (my first index).\r\n\r\nUnfortunately, related infos, to each hit of the result, is coming from an other index (address data e.g.) So now I have to make a search (automatically and via input field) to the second index, with the value from the hits to trigger a second search for each hit to an other index.",
