    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "If I understand correctly, for each result from your first index you want to do a secondary search. In that case, maybe you could use the [connector for the hits](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/connectors/connectHits.html). This way you can trigger another search for each of the result. ",
